From d8fc208f151990be5a20ce2fe0108a18e21b6138 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Mar 2026 17:04:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: trigger CI/CD deploy on current default branch

The repo has no 'main' branch - default is claude/fix-api-communication-error-EfR6w.
Without this fix, pushes never trigger the deploy workflow.

https://claude.ai/code/session_01JkY1R8XGLDV8DP5uJ5DKaz
---
 .github/workflows/deploy.yml | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/.github/workflows/deploy.yml b/.github/workflows/deploy.yml
index 142a694..2494589 100644
--- a/.github/workflows/deploy.yml
+++ b/.github/workflows/deploy.yml
@@ -4,6 +4,7 @@ on:
   push:
     branches:
       - main
+      - claude/fix-api-communication-error-EfR6w
 
 env:
   PROJECT_ID: gen-lang-client-0569062468
-- 
